Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:11.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}貴方は風のように 目を閉じては夕暮れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:17.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}何を思っているんだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:30.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}目蓋を開いていた 貴方の目はビイドロ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:37.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}少しだけ晴るの匂いがした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:48.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}晴れに晴れ、花よ咲け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:52.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}咲いて晴るのせい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:57.12,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}降り止めば雨でさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:02:02.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}貴方を飾る晴る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:07.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}胸を打つ音よ凪げ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:11.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕ら晴る風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:15.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}あの雲も越えてゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:20.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}遠くまだ遠くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:11.24,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你像風兒一樣 閉上雙眼卻是黃昏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:17.16,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}此刻你究竟在想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:30.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}望向遠方的你 眼眸好似彩色琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:37.14,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}讓人感到些許 晴天味道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:48.45,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}晴日春又晴 花兒盛放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:52.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}花開怪春晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:57.12,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}春晴風漸和 雨也是晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.12,0:02:02.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}點點灑落你身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:07.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}胸中的浪濤 快快平息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:11.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我們好似晴風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:15.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}要吹過天際的雲彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:20.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}去最遙遠的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:53.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}And I'm alright (I'll be alright)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:56.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Yeah I hear you (I care about you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:23:01.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}伸びた髪を風がからかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:04.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}全部意味があるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:06.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}立ち止まった日々も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:13.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今さらわかってあなたに追いついたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:17.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ほら　この目じゃなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}見えなかったものが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:25.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どうして 溢れてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:26.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}せめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:31.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}会いたいよ なんて言わないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:32.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ねえ　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:37.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今日だけは 思い出していいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:38.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:43.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}あなたとまた巡りあったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:48.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}もう迷わない 今を選ぶんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:54.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どこにいても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:57.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑って見せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}目を閉じれば いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:03.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}絶対なんてなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:06.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつでも届いているから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:09.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}その涙だって大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}きっと夜が明けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:19.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}I'm whispering our lullaby by for you to come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:53.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我一切都好(我會好的)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:56.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}是 我聽得到(我想念你)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:23:01.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}風兒纏繞著你變長的頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:04.32,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}一切的一切都有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:06.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就連那些止步不前的日子也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:13.53,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就算知道遲了 我也追上了你的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.03,0:23:17.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}看 如果不是這雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.54,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就看不見的那些事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:25.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}為什麼 會充盈眼眶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:26.46,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}起碼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:31.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我不會說出想要見你之類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:32.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:37.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}至少今天 我可以思念你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:38.14,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:43.15,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}倘若能和你再度邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:48.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我不會再猶豫 一定會選擇當下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:54.45,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:57.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}讓我看到笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只要閉上雙眼 就一直
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:03.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}即便我們間從沒有絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:06.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我們也早就心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:09.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}流下淚水也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.55,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}長夜定會迎來黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:19.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我輕聲吟唱著搖籃曲 期盼你能歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.70,Preview,,0,1000,0,,{\fad(300,300)}大致成型了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.01,0:24:22.50,Preview,,1000,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}來制定作戰計劃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:24.16,Preview,,1000,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\an8}原來你知道更多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.97,0:24:24.16,Preview,,0,1000,0,,{\fad(300,300)}要不要合作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.60,0:24:25.70,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}還是道歉比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.48,0:24:25.70,Preview,,1200,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}實在是不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.74,0:24:26.65,Preview,,0,1200,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那東西可沒有弱點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.16,0:24:27.41,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}看起來好像很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:29.84,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\1c&H080107&\t(146,146,\1c&HDEE5E2&)}芙莉蓮致命的破綻
